          <title>
            <string language="hu-HU">A gizai piramisok. Hátulról előre: Kheopsz piramisa, Khephrén piramisa, Mükerinosz piramisa, Mükerinosz szatelitpiramisai, IV. dinasztia, Giza.</string>
            <string language="en-US">Pyramids of Giza. From the Back to the Front: Pyramid of Khufu Pyramid of Khafre, Pyramid of Menkaure, Satellite Pyramides of Menkaure, 4th Dynasty, Giza.</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Pyramiden von Giza. Von zurück zu der 
Frontseite: Pyramide der Khufu Pyramide von Khafre, Pyramide von
Menkaure, Satellitenpyramides von Menkaure, 4. Dynastie, Giza.</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Pyramides de Giza. Du de nouveau à l'avant 
: Pyramide de pyramide de Khufu de Khafre, pyramide de Menkaure,
Pyramides satellite de Menkaure, 4ème dynastie, Giza.</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Pirâmides de Giza. Da parte traseira à 
parte dianteira: Pirâmide da pirâmide de Khufu de Khafre, 
pirâmide de Menkaure, Pyramides satellite de Menkaure, ô dynasty, 
Giza.</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Piramidi di Giza. Dal di nuovo alla parte 
anteriore: Piramide della piramide di Khufu di Khafre, piramide 
di Menkaure, Pyramides satellite di Menkaure, quarto dynasty, Giza.</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Πυραμίδες Giza. Από πίσω στο μέτωπο: 
Πυραμίδα της πυραμίδας Khufu Khafre, πυραμίδα 
Menkaure, δορυφορικό Pyramides Menkaure, 4$η δυναστεία, 
Giza.</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Pirámides de Giza. De de nuevo al frente: 
Pirámide de la pirámide de Khufu de Khafre, pirámide de 
Menkaure, Pyramides basado en los satélites de Menkaure, 4ta 
dinastía, Giza.</string>
